html:
Venti is a free spirited, wine-loving bard in Mondstadt and the current mortal vessel of Barbatos, the Anemo Archon.

  • 5 star
  • Anemo Vision

An extremely ancient bow that has retained its power despite its original master being long gone. It draws power from everyone and everything in the world, and the further away you are from that which your heart desires, the more powerful it is.

  • 5 star

The soul of the Knights of Favonius. Millennia later, it still calls on the winds of swift justice to vanquish all evil—just like the last heroine who wielded it.

Description: Leaves in the Wind - Kaedehara Kazuya
html:
A wandering samurai of the once-famed Kaedehara Clan, Kazuha is a temporary crewmember of The Crux.

html:
An educational tome written by anonymous early inhabitants who worshiped the wind. It has been blessed by the wind for its faithfulness and influence over the millennia.

Description: The Dark Side of Dawn - Diluc
html:
Born into the affluent Ragnvindr Clan, Diluc is the current owner of the Dawn Winery and a nobleman of high esteem in Mondstadt society. While a past incident caused him to split ways with the Knights of Favonius, he continues to protect Mondstadt in his own way
